Package: AntsNet
Title: Demonstrating the Isomorphism Between Ant Colony Generational Learning
    and Neural Networks
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ernest", "Fokoué", email = "epfeqa@rit.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Gregory", "Babbitt", email = "gabsbi@rit.edu", role = "aut"),
    person("Yuval", "Levental", email = "yhl3051@rit.edu", role = "aut"))
Description: Implements both Generational Ant Colony Learning (GACL) and a
    simple neural network trained with stochastic gradient descent, along with
    visualization and comparison tools that demonstrate the mathematical
    isomorphism between the two systems.  Accompanies Part III of the trilogy
    "Isomorphic Functionalities between Ant Colony and Ensemble Learning."
